<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='335817' id='t-335817'>and see results right away.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 5:48
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='337568' id='t-337568'>So it's really now a matter of taking
