<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='348116' id='t-348116'>are the simplest solutions.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='349935' id='t-349935'>And two years ago, even,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='353149' id='t-353149'>this project would not have happened,</span>
