</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 6:16
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='365158' id='t-365158'>And so the question I ask all
of you today is: why wait?</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='368425' id='t-368425'>Together, we can build the future today.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 6:22
</data>
